            "text": "\"Ken and Marci do not anticipate insurance covering the majority of their loss. Anything you can spare to help a truly great couple would be much appreciated. Any and all proceeds will go directly to Ken and Marci to pay for clothes, supplies, housing, etc and help them get back on their feet during this unexpected disaster. Thank you.\"",
