        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The fire chief, who was directing traffic out of the neighborhood, told the Albers that no trucks were available to battle the fire because they were all out battling the fire in Lake Berryessa.",
